---
title: Deconstructed Ratatouille with Balsamic Tomatoes, Feta and Garlicky Ciabatta
description: The definition of deconstructed is ‘to reduce something to its constituent parts’. We’re not sure we agree completely with this - we wouldn’t say there is any reduction going on here. This dish is such a showstopper, that we wanted to let everything from the ratatouille and feta to the garlicky ciabatta, absolutely shine!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/deconstructed-ratatouille-wk52-7d30e06d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/deconstructed-ratatouille-wk52-55fb7609.pdf
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: Mediterranean
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/deconstructed-ratatouille-wk52-5819d900a7c72a527d298fb2
nutrition:
  calories: 360 kcal
  fat: 15 g
